name: Invisible concept lora
description: Concept lora for generating invisible people. Trained on Fullanime model. Lora works, but kinda buggy, you need to do additional prompting to make it work properly, write "(((no humans)))", "faceless", "headless" etc. in the positive prompt ("amputee" also helps sometimes). For now I don't know how to improve this lora
